features: 【Fast Transfer Speed】USB C and USB 3.0 card readers are used to read data from memory card and transfer it to OTG - enabled computer, tablet or smart phone. It supports data transfer speeds up to 5 Gbps and compatible with USB 2.0 and USB 1.1. It can transfer a large number of photos and files in seconds, which avoids making you wait for a long time to transfer.

【Dual Card Simultaneous Access】This card reader supports simultaneous reading of dual cards, avoiding repeated card insertion and removal, speeding up file transfer and making data access more efficient. Compatible with SD / Micro SD / TF / SDHC / SDXC / Micro SDHC / Micro SDXC / MMC cards etc.

【Immediately Plug and Play】Plug the card reader directly into your Type C / USB A device, and it can be used immediately. No additional software assistance is required, and it supports hot plugging. Available for Android, Mac OS, Chrome OS, Windows 10/ 8.1/ 8/ 7/ XP and Linux systems.

【Humanized Design】With safe and durable aluminum shell designed, effectively extend the service life. Thoughtful lanyard allows you to avoid losing the card reader while on the go. The protective cover effectively prevents abrasion and dust from entering the USB port. Its indicator light allows you conveniently check the connection status of the device.

【Wide Compatibility】This memory card reader compatible with laptops, tablets, smart phone with USB-C port, such as MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, iPad Pro 2021/ 2020/ 2018, iPad Air 4, Galaxy S22/ S21/ S20/ S10/ S9/ Note 10, Redmi Note 10 Pro/ Note 9/ Note 8, Surface Pro, Surface Book, Huawei P50/ P40/ P30/ P20, and USB A devices such as PC, Car, PS5, PS4, Xbox One, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice rugged adapter
reviews.reviewText: I bought this along with another adapter because I've had bad luck with these adapters breaking in the field. While I ultimately chose the other adapter (the Uni) as my main unit, this one works perfectly well. With covered connectors and recessed slots, it seems to hold up well in the woods.It's more compact than the Uni adapter because it doesn't have a connector cord. A downside is that without this cord, you have a rigid connection to your smartphone, which can stress if mishandled. Also, for woodland use, it would be nice if the end caps were tethered to the body, but this "feature" can be a nuisance. The caps will keep the connector ends from being damaged if this is shoved into a backpack.Finally, a small unit that supports both USB-A and USB-C is a real plus, though not so much for smartphone use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: Excellent Card Reader with Fast USB 3.0 Speeds
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the Beikell SD Card Reader and I must say, it has exceeded my expectations. The dual connector design, featuring both USB C and USB 3.0, makes it incredibly versatile and compatible with a wide range of devices.One of the standout features of this card reader is its fast USB 3.0 speeds. Transferring large files and accessing data from my memory cards has never been quicker. The high-speed data transfer rate ensures that I can quickly and effortlessly transfer photos, videos, and other files without any lag or delay.The build quality of the reader is also top-notch. It feels solid and well-made, with a sleek and compact design that makes it easy to carry around. The connectors fit snugly into my devices, providing a stable connection every time.Another aspect I love about this card reader is its compatibility with various memory card formats. Whether it's an SD, SDHC, SDXC, or even a microSD card, this reader handles them all seamlessly. I no longer need to carry multiple card readers for different memory card types, thanks to the convenience offered by the Beikell SD Card Reader.In terms of usability, this card reader couldn't be simpler. It's truly plug-and-play, requiring no additional software or drivers to be installed. I appreciate the hassle-free experience it provides, allowing me to focus on my work or leisure activities without any technical complications.Overall, I highly recommend the Beikell SD Card Reader to anyone in need of a reliable and efficient card reader. Its dual connector design, fast USB 3.0 speeds, and wide compatibility make it a must-have accessory for photographers, videographers, and anyone who frequently deals with memory cards. Trust me, you won't be disappointed with this purchase.
